_sText: This was originally a first attempt at mapping the place where I go to LAN once a month. That was pretty boring, so I spiced it up by making it dark, adding a second story, and adding breakable lights and fire doors. This is the first map I have ever made, so have fun with it! BETA version though, a real release for me would probably have HDR and reflect maps, among other things. Please tell me if you find bugs! I used several prefabs from the prefab section, so here is credit to them Office Glass by RobinTM Psy's Ladder Pack SGT_kick_ur_ass Rotating Fan Wowzorz1leeroy's Sliding doors Chillinut's Working Barbecue Here is a short video with no sound, but it is still cool
